    Journey Up the Toms River for Some Hidden Jersey Gems
</div><br><br />
<div class="writer">by Erik R. Slagle</div>
<br><br />      
    <table align="right">
        <tr>
            <td width="220" align="right"><img src="~/images/articles/bytheexit2.jpg" alt=""></td>
